105
00:08:53,352 --> 00:08:55,991
Se le considera uno
de los mejores boxeadores

106
00:08:56,272 --> 00:08:57,910
de la historia, un agresor

107
00:08:58,149 --> 00:09:00,219
tipo Dempsey, Joe Louis,

108
00:09:00,485 --> 00:09:01,759
Kocky Marciano,

109
00:09:01,986 --> 00:09:04,056
Joe Frazier...
¿Cómo podría exactamente

110
00:09:04,698 --> 00:09:07,770
